# assets/images

> Editable SVG wireframes live under `docs/assets/images/`. The repo-root
> `assets/images/` folder is reserved for raw binary assets (real
> screenshots, source files) that are not yet ready to be served by the
> docs site.

Reference SVGs from docs pages with relative paths, e.g.:

```markdown
![Workshop app sidebar](assets/images/sidebar.svg)
```
